Post install for VIM

Get pathogen file
curl -so pathogen.vim https://raw.github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen/HEAD/autoload/pathogen.vim

Get nerd tree
git submodule add https://github.com/vim-scripts/The-NERD-tree.git bundle/nerdtree

Add ctags
sudo apt-get install exuberant-ctags

Add tag list
git submodule add https://github.com/vim-scripts/taglist.vim.git bundle/taglist

Add snipmate
git submodule add https://github.com/msanders/snipmate.vim.git bundle/snipmate

Init sub module after retrieve from github
git submodule --init update
